<span id="freeTextContainer18159215794566245511">Catholic. Writer. Lay Dominican. I write books about gods &amp; death &amp; girls with knives. Latest: ENDLESS WATER, STARLESS SKY.<br/><br/>Goodreads policies: I do read messages. I seldom friend people. I never comment on reviews of my own work.</span>

